data.title: This Stranger Things Pop-Up Book is the Most Insane Pop-Up Book I’ve Ever Seen
data.meta_description: I've been a fan of Stranger Things as soon as it first hit Netflix. It was the first show I ever binged an entire season in one sitting. Maybe you did, too.
data.text:
I've been a fan of Stranger Things as soon as it first hit Netflix. It was the first show I ever binged an entire season in one sitting. Maybe you did, too. Stranger Things merchandise have been top selling items for the past few years and, fortunately, they made a pop up book for sale.

Just like Stranger Things isn't your ordinary show, this is not your ordinary pop-up book. It's not just a single folded tree that unfolds in the middle, this book is very intricate and I'm amazed by it every time I take a look. So much so I thought I'd share it with you page-by-page.

You can find this Stranger Things book on Amazon.
